data.description: Beautiful home with an enclosed pool on the golf course in the Holley By The Sea community! With great views of the 5th & 6th holes at The Club at Hidden Creek, this property showcases several amenities throughout. The exterior includes a new roof (2022), a screen enclosed pool that has been resurfaced & has a new pool pump, and a large covered patio with an entrance to owner’s suite. The interior features beautiful arches & bullnose corners, wood & tile floors, and an eat-in kitchen with double ovens, Corian countertops with custom sink, & new refrigerator (2022). The property has a whole house generator serviced yearly and a new hot water heater (2022). The property is within five miles of Eastbay K-8 school and a short drive away from the Holley By The Sea Recreation Center.
